      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age in several areas. The exterior has noticeable scratches, a few small dents on the passenger side, and some fading paint on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there is a small tear in the driver's seat, though all electronics and the air conditioning remain fully functional. Mechanically, it has been regularly serviced and runs well, but prospective buyers should expect some minor oil seepage and the need for new tires in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for dependable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
