    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "Up for sale is a dependable vehicle in good overall condition, ideal for anyone seeking a reliable daily driver. Mechanically, the car is in great shape with a consistent service history, ensuring it starts and runs smoothly. While it shows some minor signs of normal use on the interior and a few light scratches on the exterior, it has been well-maintained and remains very presentable. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles on the road.",
