    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a dedicated fixer-upper? This vehicle is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid to roll up their sleeves! While it's in poor condition and needs some significant TLC both mechanically and cosmetically, it offers a fantastic opportunity to get on the road at a fraction of the usual cost. It\u2019s a great choice for a mechanic or a hobbyist looking for their next rewarding challenge!",
